{"title":"Eruda 網頁源始碼在線檢查器","uid":"7886689258f5f1c389497f38397efb3d","slug":"eruda-online-web-inspect-tool","date":"2021-08-05T06:28:00.000Z","updated":"2022-12-27T04:38:53.419Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/eruda-online-web-inspect-tool.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<p>相信大家都知道，在桌上電腦利用滑鼠點擊右鍵會釋出選項界面，點擊「<strong>檢視原始碼」</strong> 或於網頁鏈結的 HTTP 或 HTTPS 協定的前綴加上 <code>view-source:</code> 可以檢視目前網頁所編寫的編碼，如 HTML、JavaScript 等編碼，但我們<strong>往往不能利用它檢視更詳細的資訊</strong>。有見於此，Google Chrome 開發了一個原始碼檢查器。</p>\n<p>Google Chrome 桌上網頁版以及軟件都提供一個原始碼檢查器，用戶只需要點擊實體鍵盤上的「F12」鍵，即可呼喚它出來。可是，這個功能並<strong>沒有兼容手機版本</strong>的 Google Chrome，但這不代表我們不能嚐一嚐這玩意。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/eruda-online-web-inspect-tool/img1.jpeg\" alt=\"img1\">\\</p>\n<p>最近，我找到一個 JavaScript 編碼，是用以直接呼喚該程序顯示於網頁上，雖然，這工具<strong>並非還原的相當完整</strong> ，但基本的功能都是支援的。</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"預備適合的瀏覽器\"><a href=\"#預備適合的瀏覽器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"預備適合的瀏覽器\"></a>預備適合的瀏覽器</h1><p>先從 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.android.chrome\">Google Play 商店</a> 或 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/google-chrome/id535886823\">App Store</a> 下載 Google Chrome 瀏覽器，並把其開啟。（<strong>此功能或許不適用予其他瀏覽器）</strong></p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"新增書籤\"><a href=\"#新增書籤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"新增書籤\"></a>新增書籤</h1><p>隨便輸入一個網址，導向一個網站，然後，在左上角的<strong>豎式三點圖標</strong>內，點擊 <strong>「加入標籤」</strong> ，若手機用戶，則點擊<strong>空心星星圖標</strong>。</p>\n<p>完成後，會顯示該書籤已成功加入。這時候，我們可以編輯該書籤。</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"編輯書籤並加入-JavaScript-編碼\"><a href=\"#編輯書籤並加入-JavaScript-編碼\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"編輯書籤並加入 JavaScript 編碼\"></a>編輯書籤並加入 JavaScript 編碼</h1><p>把網址修改為以下編碼並把<code>名稱</code>修改為任意名稱，如輸入「Inspect」，並於網址的輸入框中加入以下編碼。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">javascript:\n  (function () &#123;\n    %C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0\n    var script &#x3D; %C2%A0\n    document.createElement(&#39;script&#39;);\n    %C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0\n    script.src&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;npm&#x2F;eruda&quot;;\n    %C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0\n    document.body.appendChild(script); \n    %C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0\n    script.onload &#x3D; function () &#123;\n      %C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0\n      eruda.init()\n      %C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0\n    &#125;\n  &#125;)();</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"使用方式\"><a href=\"#使用方式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用方式\"></a>使用方式</h1><p>在瀏覽器上方的搜尋框輸入「Inspect」（這是剛剛所命名的任意名稱），點擊確定便會出現該工具的懸浮圖標，點擊它便會出現其懸浮視窗。<strong>（若重新加載目前網頁，懸浮視窗會自動關閉，需要再次呼喚書籤）</strong></p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">注意</p>\n<p>iOS 或 iPad 裝置或許需要點擊書籤直接呼喚，而不是輸入「Inspect」。</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"總結\"><a href=\"#總結\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"總結\"></a>總結</h1><p>這個程序提供了許多功能，如<strong>檢視標示屬性、控制台，實時偵錯</strong>等，就由大家自己發掘嘍～</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/eruda-online-web-inspect-tool/img2.jpeg\" alt=\"img1\"></p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">注意</p>\n<p>Eruda 線上檢查器不能應用於本地網址的網頁。</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<p>更多關於 Eruda 線上網頁檢查器可 <a href=\"https://eruda.liriliri.io/\" target=\"_blank\">按此</a>。</p>\n","text":"相信大家都知道，在桌上電腦利用滑鼠點擊右鍵會釋出選項界面，點擊「檢視原始碼」 或於網頁鏈結的 HTTP 或 HTTPS 協定的前綴加上 view-source: 可以檢視目前網頁所編寫的編碼，如 HTML、JavaScript 等編碼，但我們往往不能利用它檢視更詳細的資訊。有見於...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.4k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"網頁開發","slug":"網頁開發","count":7,"path":"api/categories/網頁開發.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":4,"path":"api/tags/JavaScript.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A0%90%E5%82%99%E9%81%A9%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%E7%80%8F%E8%A6%BD%E5%99%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">預備適合的瀏覽器</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E6%9B%B8%E7%B1%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">新增書籤</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%B7%A8%E8%BC%AF%E6%9B%B8%E7%B1%A4%E4%B8%A6%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5-JavaScript-%E7%B7%A8%E7%A2%BC\"><span class=\"toc-text\">編輯書籤並加入 JavaScript 編碼</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">使用方式</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\">總結</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"BlueWhaleYT","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://i.ibb.co/zRvn96K/20210718-233824.jpg","link":"/","description":"Everything is possible, as long as you are powerful.","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"編寫 Python 並建立 Discord 機器人","uid":"045c39994454c705bd68e7054c50779a","slug":"develop-python-discord-bot","date":"2021-08-24T09:30:52.000Z","updated":"2022-12-27T04:46:14.183Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/develop-python-discord-bot.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.ibb.co/k5L4hcN/discord-cover.jpg","text":" 提示 此文案是從我的 Gitbook 搬運過來的，現在它不再被使用。 Discord 機器人的功能繁多，往往能夠令到伺服器變得多元化。人家能夠做出如此強大的機器人，你有沒有想到，你也可以編寫自己的 Discord 機器人！ 在本教學，你將會學會怎樣使用手機，編寫 Python ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.7k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Discord 開發","slug":"Discord-開發","count":4,"path":"api/categories/Discord-開發.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Python","slug":"Python","count":4,"path":"api/tags/Python.json"},{"name":"終端機指令","slug":"終端機指令","count":5,"path":"api/tags/終端機指令.json"}],"author":{"name":"BlueWhaleYT","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://i.ibb.co/zRvn96K/20210718-233824.jpg","link":"/","description":"Everything is possible, as long as you are powerful.","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{}}